flowchart TD
  Strategy[Strategic Objective] --> CSF[Critical Success Factors]
  CSF --> CIS[Critical Information Set]
  CIS --> KPI[KPI Dictionary]
  KPI --> Dashboard[Dashboard / Scorecard]
  Dashboard --> Review[Operating Review Cadence]
  Review --> Decision[Decision / Risk Acceptance / Investment]
  Decision --> Action[Improvement Backlog]
  Action --> Evidence[Evidence Of Improvement]
  Evidence --> Dashboard

  RCA[Root Cause Analysis] --> Action
  Incentives[Incentive And Goodhart Check] --> KPI
  Audit[Evidence / Audit Trail] --> Dashboard
